<item>
            <title>[LU-1867] replay-single test_89: @@@@@@ FAIL: 4 blocks leaked</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1867</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hit this problem on Maloo test on latest master branch:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/07148716-fae1-11e1-a03c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/07148716-fae1-11e1-a03c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is similiar with ORI-412 reported on Orion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test logs of test_89 attached.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
